Usage: analyze_paths_by_hier_port [-help] {{-gen_hier_file <string> [-out_file <string> ]} | {-load_hier_file <string>}} [-master <string>]

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
-gen_hier_file <string>          # Generates hier ports fanin/fanout file when
                                 # the database is available based on the given
                                 # InstanceName_list. (string, optional)
-load_hier_file <string>         # Uses a previously saved hier ports
                                 # fanin/fanout file when the database is not
                                 # available. (string, optional)
-master <string>                 # Specifies that the timing paths should be
                                 # categorized only for the specified master
                                 # category. (string, optional)
-out_file <string>               # Specifies the generated hier ports
                                 # fanin/fanout file name. (string, optional)